\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs16\b\insrsid2427393 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 Project Title:- Self Driving Car with\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506  Driver Drowsiness Detection and Alert System using Python
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af43\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \f43\fs24\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid2427393 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sb263\sa263\sl360\slmult1\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid13982704 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af43\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \f43\fs24\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid12725056 \hich\af43\dbch\af31505\loch\f43 
The Self-Driving Car Project revolutionizes transportation by incorporating neural networks for autonomous vehicle control. This application utilizes advanced machine learning algorithms to process sensor data, recognize road conditions, and make real-tim
\hich\af43\dbch\af31505\loch\f43 e driving decisions. The neural networks' ability to adapt to dynamic environments and diverse scenarios ensures safe and efficient autonomous driving. This project represents a significant stride 
\hich\af43\dbch\af31505\loch\f43 towards the future of transportation, where vehicles can navigate without human intervention, enhancing road safety and transportation efficiency.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af43\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f43\fs24\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid13260272\charrsid13982704 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\sa200\sl276\slmult1\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid13260272 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid13260272 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid14758354 \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 Self-Driving}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid13260272 \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 
 Car Project using Machine Learning}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid14758354 \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 , In this project user \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 can\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37  upload 
\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 image or \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 videos\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37  \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 to ML model and it will detects \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 road\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 
 lane, traf\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 fic signs and autono\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 m\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 ous\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37  steering \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 ac\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 
cording to curve. \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 Simultaneously\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37  it wi\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 ll identify the person drowsiness\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37  state an\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 d it wo
\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 rks on real\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 -time. \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 It \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 is desktop based softw\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 are developed using 
\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 tkinter\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37  library.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid13260272 
\par 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 Object detection is essential for self-driving vehicles to comprehend their environment. The
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 
paper proposes an RVnet model which will be used for improving real-time detection efficiency. RVnet blends convolutional and recurrent neural networks to represent spatial connections between video frames. To extract visual data every frame, model will e
\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 mploy a CNN backbone pretrained on ImageNet. These can be fed into an LSTM recurrent layer, which will be able to collect data across frames. We will improve RVne\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 
t to recognize items such as automobiles, pedestrians, and bicycles for autonomous driving. The RVnet model classifies detections produced by region proposal networks. By using KITTI, Waymo, and nuScenes dataset, the RVnet model can increase average accur
\hich\af37\dbch\af31505\loch\f37 acy. The improved accuracy and fast speed will show RVnet's potential for improving real-time object recognition in self-driving vehicle applications.
\par 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f3\fs20\insrsid2427393\charrsid2427393 \loch\af3\dbch\af31505\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}}\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-360\li720\ri0\sb100\sa100\sbauto1\saauto1\widctlpar
\jclisttab\tx720\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\ls1\adjustright\rin0\lin720\itap0\pararsid2427393 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24 \ltrch\fcs0 \f0\fs24\insrsid2427393\charrsid2427393 \hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 
https://www.cvlibs.net/datasets/kitti/index.php
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f3\fs20\insrsid2427393\charrsid2427393 \loch\af3\dbch\af31505\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 https://waymo.com/open/
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\ltrpar \rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \f3\fs20\insrsid2427393\charrsid2427393 \loch\af3\dbch\af31505\hich\f3 \'b7\tab}\hich\af0\dbch\af31505\loch\f0 https://www.nuscenes.org/nuscenes
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \li0\ri0\sa200\sl276\slmult1\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid13260272 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af37 \ltrch\fcs0 \f37\lang9\langfe1033\langnp9\insrsid2427393 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs16\b\insrsid2427393 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 Intro Real-Time Self Driving System using Deep Learning Project:-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2427393 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 
Object detection, or the method of localizing and identifying things in images, is a critical function needed by self-driving vehicles to navigate their surroundings safely. Precisely recognizing items such as automobiles, motorcycles, road signs, people,
\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506  and so on in real-time offers critical perceptive skills for self-driving cars. Although deep learning has made tremendous progress in object identificatio\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 
n, maintaining high precision with low latency remains a problem, particularly in dynamic self-driving settings. This proposal describes research into utilising Recurrent Vision Networks (RVnet) to improve real-time object recognition in self-driving vehi
\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 cle applications. RVnet trains spatio-temporal abstractions from consecutive input by combining convolutional neural networks (}{\field\fldedit{\*\fldinst {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2427393 
\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506  HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Convolutional_neural_network" }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4852467 {\*\datafield 
00d0c9ea79f9bace118c8200aa004ba90b0200000003000000e0c9ea79f9bace118c8200aa004ba90b8e000000680074007400700073003a002f002f0065006e002e00770069006b006900700065006400690061002e006f00720067002f00770069006b0069002f0043006f006e0076006f006c007500740069006f006e00
61006c005f006e0065007500720061006c005f006e006500740077006f0072006b000000795881f43b1d7f48af2c825dc485276300000000a5ab000300ff}}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs17\ul\cf2\insrsid2427393 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 CNNs}}}
\sectd \ltrsect\linex0\sectdefaultcl\sftnbj {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2427393 \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 
) with recurrent neural networks (RNNs) (Khan, Lee and Lim, 2023). RVnet models are able to include inter-frame spatial context and dependencies, resulting in improved object identification over single-frame models.
\par 
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 
The primary research tasks are as follows: 1) Create an RVnet model designed for reliable and real-time identification with appropriate categories of objects such as automobiles, pedestrians, road signs, and so on in self-driving situations. 2) Test the f
\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 ramework on self-driving vehicle dataset\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 
s such as KITTI, Waymo, and nuScenes to evaluate efficiency contrary to single-frame baselines. 3) Examine the effect of various RVnet designs and hyper-parameters on identification speed and reliability. 4) Deploy and analyze the model on an embedded sys
\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 tem for a real autonomous automobile.
\par 
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 
The fundamental approach entails using a CNN backbone for spatial extracting features, adding RNN layers to collect inter-frame data, producing area suggestions, and training the RVnet model for 2 classification and bo
\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 x-bound regression. Extensive studies will assess RVnet settings, improve performance vs. accuracy constraints, and benchmark on public datasets as well as practical test cars.
\par 
\par \hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 
The goal of this study is to illustrate RVnet's potential for improving real-time object perception for self-driving cars. RVnet offers the ability to enhance detection accuracy without sacrificing inference performance or latency by merging deep spatial 
\hich\af31506\dbch\af31505\loch\f31506 feature learning with temporal sequence modeling. This study has the potential to make significant contributions to the development of secure and reliable computer vision algorithms for autonomous vehicles.
\par 
